===

title: TraffickerDismissal
---
ShadyTrafficker: Hello, hello. Well, come on in. 
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Do you have any Harvested Cores to sell to me? I'll buy any you have.
<<complete_objective DialogueCommands "VisitCoreTrader">>
-> No I haven't got any.
    <<if !$traffickerGaveJob001>>
        ShadyTrafficker: Alright. Come see me if you get some. You wouldn't be looking for work?
            -> No.
            -> Yes.
                <<jump OfferJobInChokedCaverns>>
    <<else>>
        ShadyTrafficker: Alright. Come see me if you get some.
    <<endif>>
-> Yes, I have some to sell.
    <<start_shopping_sell_illegal DialogueCommands "ShadyCoreTrafficker">>
    -> Alright, I'm done.
    <<stop_shopping_sell DialogueCommands "ShadyCoreTrafficker">>
    ShadyTrafficker: See ya round.
<<if !$traffickerGaveJob001>>
-> Actually, I'm looking for work..
    <<jump OfferJobInChokedCaverns>>
<<endif>>
===

title: OfferJobInChokedCaverns
---
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Sure, sure. I do have something.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: I have a facility in the abandoned mine real close to here.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: I need someone to replace the RTG that keeps the place running.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: And I happen to know that down there are two valuable core groves.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Get them and harvest them in my facility.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Come back here. I'll reward you nicely for the Cores you find and the favor.
-> I will think about it.
    ShadyCoreTrafficker: I'll be here if you change your mind.
-> Yes, count me in. 
    ShadyCoreTrafficker: Excellent. 
    <<add_objective DialogueCommands "VisitChokedCavernMine">>
    <<activate_objective DialogueCommands "VisitChokedCavernMine">>
    <<add_objective DialogueCommands "InstallNewRTGInGenerator">>
    <<activate_objective DialogueCommands "InstallNewRTGInGenerator">>
    <<give_player_item DialogueCommands "RTGNuclearBattery" 1>>
    <<set $traffickerGaveJob001 = true>>
    -> Ok, I'll be off.
        ShadyCoreTrafficker: Yeah, ok friend.
    -> Anything I should know?
        <<jump QuestionAboutChokedCaverns>>

===

title: QuestionAboutChokedCaverns
---
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Yeah, it's pretty contaminated these days.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: But not to worry! My facility has a decontamination tank.
ShadyCoreTrafficker: Move fast and don't hang around, you'll be fine.
-> Thanks...
