title: CoresTraffickerIntro
---
<<declare $trafficker_rep = 0>>
ShadyTrafficker: Hey, fella, how's the Minnas been treatin' you? I take it you know why you're here, talkin' to me, ya?
-> I know you traffic in illegal core harvests. I've come to shut you down for good.
    <<set $trafficker_rep = $trafficker_rep - 2>>
    <<jump PlayerThreatensTrafficker>>
-> Yeah, you deal in illegal alien Sheol AI cores? How do I know I can trust you?
    <<jump PlayerQuestionsTraffickerTrust>>
-> Yeah I'm here to get down to business.
ShadyTrafficker: You don't say... 
    <<scoffs>>
    <<initiate_trade>>
